## Project: {{PROJECT_NAME}}

## Common Commands

```bash
make lint      # Lint all components
make test      # Test all components
make build     # Build all components
make clean     # Clean all artifacts
make help      # Show all targets
```

## Git Hooks

Hooks are automatically configured. They run on:
- **Pre-commit**: Lint on staged files
- **Pre-push**: Tests and build on changed directories

## Code Style

- Ensure code passes `make lint` before committing
- Tests should pass before pushing
